Step: inventory-step
Title: Inventory - enumerate migration targets and group into batches
Role: implementer
Accepted verdicts: accept

Context (from reads):
--- reports/migrate/brief.json ---
{
  "objective": "migrate: replace a small legacy API",
  "source": "Existing implementation referenced by: migrate: replace a small legacy API",
  "target": "Replacement implementation requested by: migrate: replace a small legacy API",
  "scope": "migrate: replace a small legacy API",
  "success_criteria": [
    "Demonstrate the migration addresses: migrate: replace a small legacy API"
  ],
  "coexistence_appetite": "short-window",
  "rollback_plan": "Revert the batch sub-run commit; the pre-migration source still works because coexistence kept it in place.",
  "verification_command_candidates": [
    {
